<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire has not typically been an important disturbance factor because stands often lack enough vegetation cover to carry a fire. However, both fire and non-native plants such as <i>Bromus rubens </i>are increasingly becoming threats to this alliance, and these plants act as principal fuels for fires. Early seral vegetation will dominate for a number of years before shrubs re-establish post-fire.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
